name: AghoriPUNK
description:
DeathMONKpunk Series. Number 1 Aghori Punk - Aghoris are a sect of Holy Men in India. Usually found in cremation grounds they keep human skulls to use as bowls.   Aghor means that which is simple. They view all of reality as God. No high or low, good or bad, clean or dirty. All is One. 

Also, they follow no rules, use intoxicants in their rituals, and generally have soft hearts of compassion for humanity. Which is quite Punk.

AUM MA KRING is a mantra to the Divine Mother Kali
